---
title: Speedy Lamb, Spinach & Feta Rissoles with Pita Bread Garden Salad
description: These simple rustic rissoles are packed with moisture and flavour from spinach and feta. They’re the perfect little parcels of joy to be savoured with a simple Greek-style pita salad and a herbed mayonnaise.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5be241b5ae08b565032d4b72-e99d12bf.jpg
